n Ästhetik und Anthropologie“ gesprochen worden. Worin genau sie besteht, klärt dieses Buch.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aAestheticsxStudy and teachingzGermanyxHistoryy18th century. 0aAesthetics, Moderny18th century. 0aAnthropologyxHistoryy18th century. 0aArtsxStudy and teachingzGermanyxHistoryy18th century. 0aEducationzGermanyxPhilosophyxHistoryy18th century. 4aAnthropologie. 4aHalle (Saale). 4aJahrhundert, 18. / Literatur. 4aLiteraturwissenschaft. 4aPhilosophie. 4aÄsthetik. 70(DE-588)4000626-80(DE-627)1064005410(DE-576)208838821aÄsthetik2gnd 70(DE-588)4002230-40(DE-627)10639410X0(DE-576)208846212aAnthropologie2gnd 70(DE-588)4003524-40(DE-627)1043068310(DE-576)208851976aAufklärung2gnd 70(DE-588)4045791-60(DE-627)1062002590(DE-576)209066873aPhilosophie2gnd 70(DE-588)4059758-10(DE-627)1041314460(DE-576)209132159aTheologie2gnd 70(DE-588)4061778-60(DE-627)1061345580(DE-576)20914114XaUniversität2gnd 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / German.2bisacsh  a18th Century/Literature.  aAesthetics.  aAnthropology.  aHalle (Saale).  aLiterary Studies.  aPhilosophy.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Literary and Cultural Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110637854oZDB-23-GLC08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2010z9783110233544oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET LINGUISTIK UND LITERATURWISSENSCHAFT  2010z9783110233605oZDB-23-DGA0 cprintz978311025126540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311025127240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110251272423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110251272/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  